org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.viz

Class Visualization

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.viz.Visualization
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ExperimentObserver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CartPoleVisualization, MountainCarVisualization, PoleSwingUpVisualization

    public abstract class Visualization
extends Object
implements ExperimentObserver, Serializable
    Abstract class that helps to implement a visualization of an environment The derived classes must only implement the visualize() method. See MountainCarVisualization for an example.
